                       Global Change Program
                      </a>
                     </strong>
                    </li>
                   </ul>
                   <figure class="caption caption-img" role="group">
                    <img alt="Carbon Drawdown in Georgia" data-entity-type="file" data-entity-uuid="79b7255d-38c3-4f9a-aa65-284b35f03248" src="/sites/default/files/inline-images/Group%20Photo.jpg">
                     <figcaption>
